HEADWORD: Lemna
<hw>Lemna</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A genus of minute aquatic herbs
floating on or below the water surface of still water consisting of a
leaflike frond or plant body and single root.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> genus <gen>Lemna</gen>.</syn>⟦br⟧
